# Remember to never publicly share your keystore.
# See https://flutter.dev/to/reference-keystore
key.properties
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks
# Exception: the SHARED debug-only keystore is committed on purpose so all devs +
# CI sign debug builds with one certificate (a single SHA-1 to register for Google
# sign-in). Debug only — never commit a release keystore.
!app/debug.keystore
